Mia is the lead guitarist. She has lived abroad for 5 years since when she was a child due to her parents' business.
Being a playful only daughter, she doesn't like to be alone and likes to hang out with people.

She said, "I had to hide and control my feeling after my debut, but it's really hard. Because I'm so honest with my feeling."
